    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Some websites are using collapsing widgets to be able to have a lot of widgets without messing up the display. Thus always rendering widgets was not efficient since a lot of them were collapsed.\n\nMaybe we should not use the `shouldComponentUpdate` for that then. Maybe just not render the `ComposedComponent` when it is collapsed.\n",
